    "body": "Problem:\n\nvim.iter annotations were too opaque, and the generated help did not\nexplain generic Iter and ArrayIter types clearly.\n\nSolution:\n\nAdd explicit generics to Iter and ArrayIter, tighten the annotations for\narray-only methods and multi-value pipelines, and update the luacats\nparser, vimdoc generation, and tests so the generated help preserves\nthose types.\n\nAI-assisted: Codex\n",
